    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 flex items-center">
        <span class="bg-red-500 w-2 h-8 mr-3"></span>
        Recommended For You
